@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
@section Header {
    <h1>@ViewBag.Title</h1>
}
<div class="about">
    <div class="row icon-row">

        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <span>
                    <img src="~/Images/noun_189153_cc compass.svg" /> @*Created by Jems Mayor from the Noun Project*@
                </span>
                <h3>Quality</h3>
                <p>We construct every piece of equipment with care and precision.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <span>
                    <img src="~/Images/noun_997837_cc crown.svg" /> @*Created by Aleksandr Vector from the Noun Project*@
                </span>
                <h3>Service</h3>
                <p>Our customers know they're the most valued part of our business.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <span class="xs">
                    <img src="~/Images/noun_1023751_cc horse.svg" /> @*Created by Bakunetsu Kaito from the Noun Project*@
                </span>
                <h3>Speed</h3>
                <p>We ensure prompt delivery of even the smallest order.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-eq-height business">
        <div class="col-md-6 image">
            <div id="AboutCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="false">

                <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="item active">
                        <img src="~/Images/carousel-siegenut-base.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="~/Images/carousel-shipping.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="~/Images/carousel-logger.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Left and right controls -->
                <a class="left carousel-control" href="#AboutCarousel" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="right carousel-control" href="#AboutCarousel" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 text">
            <h2>Our Business</h2>
            <p>
                Our company started when we noticed just how hard it is to get a good battering ram in the middle of a drawn out siege.
                Our founders banded together and created SiegeNut to solve the problems of the siege industry of the day. 
            </p>
            <p>
                Our high-speed fleet of the latest ships and courier services get whatever you order to you in the fastest time possible, by land or by sea.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our trained crew of engineers and siegewrights can construct, fix, or walk you through assembling any piece of equipment on our market.
                We have the highest customer satisfaction rate among any company of our type.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row row-eq-height location">
        <div class="col-md-6 text">
            <h2>Our Location</h2>
            <p>Etiam diam lacus, tristique in quam sed, luctus posuere diam. Vivamus malesuada mi vel turpis placerat, sit amet venenatis dui suscipit. 
            Curabitur mollis sapien vel urna dictum, et fringilla sem ornare. Suspendisse dignissim ac nibh eget consequat. Vestibulum pharetra tellus 
            lacus, eu iaculis sem convallis a. Quisque a congue lectus. Donec lacinia leo eget neque dapibus, eget commodo nulla porttitor. 
            Nam sagittis rhoncus urna vel aliquam. Integer bibendum molestie suscipit. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 image">
            <img src="~/Images/wales-location.png" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>